text: @senatemajldr @KellyannePolls It's time to get America Back to Business! Of the 20 counties with the most COVID19 cases, only 2 voted for Donald J. Trump in the 2016 election! Not only that, the Congressmen representing these twenty counties are all Democrats, among them, Jerry Nadler, AOC and Rashida Tlaib.
